flowchart LR
    Single["1. Single responsibility\none tool, one job"] --> Good["Good agent tool"]
    Idempotent["2. Idempotent when possible\nretries stay safe"] --> Good
    SideEffects["3. Explicit side effects\nno hidden send or write"] --> Good
    Structured["4. Structured output\nschema instead of free text"] --> Good
    Errors["5. Actionable errors\nwhat / why / how"] --> Good

    Good --> Predictable["Predictable agent behavior\nclear calls, safer retries, easier validation"]

